An '''intercom telephone''' is a special kind of [[telephone]] that controls a [[Intercom|school or an office buildings intercom system]].  For example, with that telephone, the employers make the school announcements and can call each [[classroom]]'s intercom by dialing the room number of that classroom.  It can be interfaced with the building's [[access control]] system.

