'''Koombea INC''' is an American [[Software development|digital product development]] company, established in 2007. <ref>{{cite web|last1=Richtel|first1=Matt|last2=Wortham|first2=Jenna|title=Tired of Looking for Work, Some Create Their Own|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/03/14/technology/start-ups/14startup.html|website=The New York Times|accessdate=7 March 2017|date=13 March 2009}}</ref> The company specializes in mobile and web applications based on the open-source tool [[Ruby on Rails]]. The firm has offices in [[San Francisco]] and [[New York City]] in the USA and [[Barranquilla]] in [[Colombia]], and is headquartered in [[Miami, Florida]]. It was founded by ''Jonathan Tarud'', who currently acts as the CEO of the company.<ref>{{cite web|title=Colombian startup Koombea answers demand to simplify Shopify|url=http://www.geektime.com/2015/10/13/colombian-startup-koombea-answers-demand-to-simplify-shopify/|website=Geektime|accessdate=7 March 2017|date=13 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Egusa|first1=Conrad|title=Colombia Is One Of Latin America’s Most Promising New Tech Hubs|url=https://techcrunch.com/2014/11/22/an-overview-of-colombia-one-of-latin-americas-most-promising-new-tech-hubs/|website=TechCrunch|accessdate=7 March 2017}}</ref>
The company has developed [[Software development tool|web solutions]] that equip clients with tools for sales, team and marketing management. Among them is ''Saasler'', a tool that focuses on native integration to enhance product sales and promote brand loyalty. The application also includes several integration intelligence features, such as [[Access token|refreshing expired tokens]], [[API management|API throttling]], security and data encryption, and a range of analytic.<ref>{{cite web|title=SAASLER Trademark of Koombea Inc. - Registration Number 5118707 - Serial Number 87049547 :: Justia Trademarks|url=https://trademarks.justia.com/870/49/saasler-87049547.html|website=trademarks.justia.com|accessdate=7 March 2017|language=en}}</ref> ''Convergely'' is a virtual assistant developed by Koombea, which works through integration with chat apps, like Slack and HipChat.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Dove|first1=Jackie|title=Convergely, a suite of productivity tools for Slack, launches into public beta|url=https://thenextweb.com/apps/2015/07/14/convergely-a-suite-of-productivity-tools-for-slack-launches-into-public-beta/#.tnw_DwrcZYfZ|website=The Next Web|accessdate=7 March 2017|date=14 July 2015}}</ref> The company has also developed ''Dashable'', an app which builds up on the concept of [[time tracking]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Dashable Project Management|url=http://www.gleanster.com/solution/dashable-project-management|publisher=Gleanster.com|accessdate=7 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Author|first1=AppAdvice Staff|title=Dashable by Koombea, Inc.|url=https://appadvice.com/app/dashable/669216360|website=AppAdvice|accessdate=7 March 2017}}</ref>
